text.tspan: Fulness of the Spirit — As the Living Water
I have come to You. I am thirsty; let me drink!
All the riches of this life
Flood in me, with joy I cry,
Drinking at the Fount of life am I!
Though I fail each day, I return to You and pray,
Keep me always in Your grace.
Lord make home in all my heart and stay!
There is a river flowing from the throne
